title: 【#生スバル】ハッピーバレンタイン！おはすば！：FREE TALK【ホロライブ/大空スバル】
name: Oozora Subaru

entries.text: I'm a little too freshly awake.
Gonna put on some lip cream.
Guess I'll put up some free-to-use chocolate assets.
I wonder if I can bring out a Valentine's vibe.
So, I want to do the morning greetings quickly, but...
Lately, honestly... it is seriously too cold.
When I sleep, my feet end up facing the window.
Because the window side is cold on my feet, uh...
If I don't have my Yu-Gi-Oh! Kuriboh cushion, I can't sleep because of the cold.
Hey, supposedly today and tomorrow will be warm?
No, really, apparently it's warm, but...
It's pretty nice putting the Kuriboh cushion at my feet.
I fall asleep going "Ooh, fluffy fluffy warm fluffy."
No, but this time of year...
Yeah, and they say the day after tomorrow it'll go back to winter.
Uhh, I can say this with confidence.
Apparently Subaru doesn't have a smell.
It's because I take baths constantly.
Apparently I don't have a smell!
I get told that a lot.
People say "You don't smell like anything."
Apparently I just smell like fabric softener.
No, I don't really get it, but...
having particles stick to my body...
It's cold and the dryness is brutal...
I put it on while going "Aaaagh."
I like nice scents, so I like perfume, but...
"I don't want to put anything on my showered body!"
That's what I mean. That's it.
I've been trying my best to use it lately.
Mmm, I don't really like it though.
So, the fact that I love baths...
and this season where the dryness is dangerous...
So I do my best to apply it.
Getting forced to use body cream...
Like, "Guess I have to put it on..."
If I raise the humidity in the room...
I'm trying hard to raise it, but...
Like, unless I spray mist inside the house...
Mm, gotta do a rain dance.
If I do that, mold might grow...
in the bath forever is the only way.
But staying in the bath dries out your skin.
If I talk about what happened this week...
I was suffering from a toothache.
thought, "What the heck is she doing?"
I kinda understand her feelings now.
The day I got my gums stitched...
I was the hungriest I've ever been.
That day, with my gums stitched and going "Ugh,"...
I kinda wanted to eat a hamburger.
apologizing for eating a hamburger came to mind too vividly.
And as a result of remembering that too vividly...
I ate four in one day.
is when I get the most hungry.
woke up thinking "I wanna eat a sandwich"...
Maybe I was hungry *because* I wasn't feeling well?
thinking that while going "I wanna eat pasta."
So I realized I can't really...
Everyone, if you get tooth surgery or whatever...
you'll get hungry, so be careful.
and going to eat with her.
Before the toothache, Oozora Subaru was...
I was going out to eat and stuff.
So I went to eat with Kanade.
"There's something I do a lot when I talk."
"It feels weird to say this, but..."
"I caught it from Okayu," I said.
Since Subaru does it all over the place...
and I did it a lot in front of Kanade too...
"There's a theory you caught it from me."
"I don't know why, but lately I..."
"put my index finger by my face like this..."
Wah, there's a Laplus route too?
Laplus... wait, aren't there a lot of Hololive members who talk with their finger up?
No, that's why! Someone somewhere spread it!
Hey, I wonder what route it took to get there.
Well, but Laplus talking like an otaku...
No, but when Laplus is in otaku-talk mode...
I'm more concerned about her way of speaking than the finger.
How does she even talk like that?
An Index Finger Pandemic is happening.
Wait, really, if there are other Holomems...
who talk with their index finger up...
I want you to tell me.
the lip cream comes off, right?
No matter how much lip cream you applied...
"It's the end of the world" vibes.
"Just gotta eat the lip cream! Voice is crusty too!"
You have to be pretty close to do that.
is the type who can't do it.
Usually I'd say "Here," lend it, and after they apply it...
I'd usually wipe it off with a tissue.
Not that it's dirty or anything...
But doing that is rude, right?
A stranger's plastic bottle is a bit tough.
Well, I don't really get stranger's bottles anyway but...
Where exactly did this habit come from?
It's a story about Subaru's hips.
The other day when I went out with everyone...
I'm wearing them cause it's cold.
When going out to play a little...
or going to someone's house for a bit...
and even when going to work...
I wear those grey sweats a lot.
When I went out with everyone...
when they get wet with water...
it looks like a stain... it gets really huge.
it was wet, and it got on my butt.
It got all over me, and I didn't notice at all.
And Subaru thought, "What do I do?"
I stuck my butt out like "Mio-sha, is this bad?" to show her.
And Mio-sha goes "Hmm, it's slightly off-center."
Is that really the issue right now!?
What am I supposed to do!?
Is this the time to be calm about it!?
Subaru is in a "I might have leaked" situation...
I went to the toilet to check, but in the end...
Is exactly opposite to where my eyes are.
So it was too hard to confirm.
And just sat down normally again.
Hey, I wish they'd stop doing that.
I wish they'd stop doing that, seriously.
I mean, it feels weird to say this but...
I only wear those inside the house...
I don't go out in those.
There are ones specifically for going out...
By the way, I wear them until...
That's right, the ones for going out...
But the ones at home are battle-hardened veterans.
"Radish eaten in a place like this is the best."
It's the same as that concept.
In the end, this kind of thing is easiest to sleep in.
But it stains, yeah, that's true.
I want to make a list of Subaru's favorite pajamas.
told me "Those look like hospital gowns."
Subaru really liked them and wore them, but...
Ayame said "Those look like a hospital gown."
"These were hospital gowns!?" The shocking pajamas.
But Subaru has actually been hospitalized, so I know...
No, hospital gowns are more, umm...
Could you stop calling them hospital gowns?
I thought that in my heart.
"I want to become a tanned, tall..."
She has that side to her.
Uhh, Subaru said "Like hell I'd strip!"
By the way, she dropped this line...
not just in a space with Subaru and Korone...
but where there were quite a few other people.
There are things only Korone can say.
When she came to visit Subaru's house...
I think it was Hakos and Shion?
She was doing a huge Millionaire Move.
What is that, that Millionaire Move?
"If someone of Koro-san's status says so..."
No, really! Plus, there's this mysterious aura of power.
And she's just rubbing legs the whole time.
And not over clothes, she's rubbing bare legs.
Yeah, the Thigh-Rubbing Yokai, Inugami Korone.
Someone of Korone's... what is that? A meme?
"If a powerhouse like Korone says so, rub away."
Wealth, Fame, Power... Korone who acquired everything in this world.
Also, the Holomems being rubbed... a lot of them make faces like they don't hate it, which is crazy.
They were going "Ehhhh~". Saying "What are you doing~?"
Right? Exactly. If they hated it, they'd say stop or walk away...
Cute Girl Check. The Cute Girl Check is crazy.
Korone is a genius after all.
My tooth was so done for...
I was like, "Crap, can I participate?"
The fact that my tooth died...
Was after the final day's schedule was decided.
"Matching schedules for this many people is bad-py!"
I was panicking like "Bad bad bad," but...
"If it hurts, another day is totally fine."
She was saying that for me.
"Yeah, another day is totally okay," she said.
But probably, my tooth doesn't hurt *that* much.
wins out, and it often becomes...
"Eh, but since it's a big deal, another day might be better," right?
Subaru was pretty afraid of that happening.
So to convey "I'm seriously okay today"...
I said "I think I'm okay! If it's impossible, I'll join via chat."
"What's going to happen? Doki doki," I was saying.
Until then she was like "Subaru-senpai, are you okay?"
"Then we have no choice but to gooooo!"
"Then we have no choice but to gooooo!"
That kind of thing helps, seriously.
She has that side to her.
I'm glad we could defeat the Wall of Flesh.
I thought we couldn't beat it.
Mio-sha fighting with lag was too funny.
Really, no matter how many times I watch it, it's funny.
Double KO, Double KO, Double KO for Subaru.
There are too many elements Fubu-chan likes.
No, but Terraria was super fun.
It doesn't have deep meaning, but...
Does anyone know what she wants *besides* Hoshimachi Suisei?
Since I missed going the other day...
"I want to go eat oden at Azu-Iro Cafeteria!"
I really wanted to go so badly...
Even though I contacted them with unbelievable speed beforehand...
Thinking that, I couldn't go. Not talking about that.
Ah, I really just wanted to go!
And seeing it... did everyone see?
I don't really get it but...
Let me eat that pickled plum!
Haku's rice ball, calling it Iroha's rice ball...
"What are you saying?" you might feel, but...
Rice balls she makes are basically...
Haku's rice balls from Spirited Away.
I wanted to eat the fried tofu too.
I thought I caught a cold.
But it wasn't a cold, my tooth just hurt!
but apparently it was the tooth nerve.
Well, but going with a cavity is bad too.
Well, I guess I'll make it a nice veggie set.
Well, I know people will say Hoshimachi Suisei.
Just, I can't give her Hoshimachi Suisei anymore.
I couldn't take a very good picture though.
I shall give it to you.
Hey, sorry, didn't one decoration just plop off?
Mmm, I made about 8 of them...
but only these succeeded. I'm too clumsy.
It was seriously too hard, lol.
Seriously, I made these after watching Gundam...
I thought my emotions were gonna break.
Honestly, making chocolate is too hard.
While putting these bead-like sugars on...
I thought I was gonna lose my mind.
I made that thing for the first time too.
What is it... that icing stuff.
I ate quite a lot of it.
There was nothing I could eat.
The lump of sugar seriously hit the spot.
Since there was too little to eat...
I mean, I was only eating soup...
I can't chew on the left side at all...
Like a Kodama, eating like this.
You know? If food goes to the left side, it's bad.
I was eating like this but...
I was so focused on eating, I'd forget things immediately.
"Put water in the cup," I was told.
It became like that, and eventually...
"And, probably, this one I just ate has stuff on the rim."
Eating after a long time probably did that.
Maybe all the nutrition went to my stomach.
Maybe blood flow concentrated in the stomach and I couldn't think.
So, Subaru got really worried and took a health exam.
If that's true, isn't that scary?
"This happened and that happened, and lately I forget a lot..."
"Please sleep a lot. If that doesn't solve it, come back."
Lack of sleep, lack of sleep...
Is lack of sleep really the cause of all that?
"Sleep a lot okay?" I was told and came home.
I got a souvenir from Rui.
Rui went on a trip, right?
Uhh, there was definitely a duck pouch...
I'm playing Uma Musume after this but...
"What should I start with?" I asked.
but the Uma Musume talk wouldn't stop.
She teaches in just the right way.
"Yeah, it's okay to show it on stream."
I don't know if it was fast talking...
Helps a lot, helps a lot.
"like that, I'll help you," she said.
"Maybe the timing is perfect," we said.
I can't talk about it in detail but...
Subaru is pretty much moving as lead.
It's not something that will come out immediately.
What do they think we are?
In a good way, you know.
Is there a theory Subaru's perception is naive?
Has been worried that her lines are too much like One Piece's Luffy.
From the person who made corrections...
I talked a bit during Mario, but...
Lately in lines I get for sponsored streams...
"Doesn't this sound too much like Luffy from One Piece?"
"What do I do?" It's become like that.
Crap, I have too many servers...
"About the part being too much like Luffy..."
LOL. So it really is like that.
No, but it's hard, I think.
I guess at a glance, the shortcut hair...
Just the visual of the shortcut...
It's hard to grasp the image, I assume.
D is the Will of Duck.
So it can't be helped if I become Luffy.
That makes it super hard too.
I think it's one of them.
See me as a total comedian.
See me as totally Maiko (Michael Jackson).
DON! "You guys! A brand new story!"
You guys started saying Maiko Maiko!
That's right, you guys started it!
Subaru didn't think that was Maiko!
But because everyone keeps saying Maiko Maiko...
Lately my smartphone recommends Michael Jackson videos too!
Subaru is susceptible to placebo so...
There's a Michael movie in June?
Lately I've made the duck character myself...
and made goods out of it.
Has a new outfit like Michael...
If I wear that, what are you gonna do!?
I'll end up doing it! If you say things...
No no, like hell I'd Moonwalk at Fes!
If I threw in a Moonwalk that would be crazy!
Saying all that and getting hyped...
Just a moment ago it was Valentine's...
Before I knew it, we were talking about Michael.
Last week I said I would but didn't.
It's the Second Coming of Me.
I want to play a dating...
Just one thing I can say is...
I wanna play. Wanna play Tokimeki Memorial.
The period until the wish comes true...
Halfway through, I really thought that.
"No no, gathering materials is too hard!"
"Love that comes true instantly isn't love."
You should turn that into a song.
Waking up. Subaru is waking up too.
Mmm, but this time in winter makes you feel like that.
Subaru has always gotten grumpy if she can't sleep...
People who can do stuff, I respect you.
Is there anything you want me to talk about?
Didn't write a diary. Gotta write it.
No, really, one thing I can say is...
I'm glad I didn't get into debt with Pekora.
Well, I did interact with Pekora but...
Pekora's debt comes with unbelievable interest.
"So you didn't borrow only from Pekora?"
If you say "Lend me some" to Peko-chan...
Crap, doing Pekora's voice hurts my tooth a bit.
Having her give it to you is best.
Conversely, I wonder where Su-chan draws the line?
When Subaru went to Su-chan's call-in...
My tooth was all messed up so...
So I'm wondering, where is the line where Su-chan thinks "Not cute"?
"As long as it's not a character break (interpretation mismatch)."
No, Maiko is totally "cute" to her.
What does Subaru have to do to be out of character?
Okay, I'll try talking about economics.
Things you can buy with 10 yen...
With 10 yen, can you NOT buy...
By the way, before joining Hololive...
Subaru cooked for herself like crazy!
I made cookies with just water.
sent from my parents' home a lot...
Mmm, I made all sorts of things!
I can't do anything at all.
Why did it end up like that?
There's a hamburg with an egg inside.
Yeah, right. The one Luna got mad at.
I don't know the name of the dish.
I have tissues, and I even have bath salts now.
I want you to rest easy.
Did I make beef bowl too? Maybe.
The one who made Tandoori Chicken was Choco-sen.
Luna said "I don't want to soak in plain hot water."
At first I was like "What is she saying?"
Soaking in your own hot water...
in the sense of healing oneself...
making it "nice hot water" is totally valid.
I wonder if Luna can cook for herself?
I don't really have that image though.
Aren't there too many members who can do housework?
Is Subaru the only one who can't?
Everyone can do housework, it's amazing.
Subaru was just flying plastic bags...
People who can cook or do housework...
If Subaru can't do it either, it's fine!
Then whatever! Subaru can't do it either!
If a Holomem tells me that...
"Hah? Sora-chan is the same, you know!"
Someone to do it... after all...
I want to do it but...
If Sora-chan started doing it, she'd probably be really good.
It would take 3 years of training.
But if Sora-chan decides "I'll cook now!"
Yeah. Subaru is going to cooking class.
It's better to ask someone skilled, definitely.
The best, the best, the best, the best!
It's fine. There are skilled people...
Unskilled people leave it to housekeepers.
I was able to make chocolate!
As you can see from this...
If I try hard, I can do it.
As an ecological feature of Oozora Subaru...
Fold laundry? Like hell I will! I can't fold!
I can do it if I try!
Actually, I had one more worry.
When I went to get my hair cut...
You can read magazines on tablets, right?
Huge, so people can see what you're reading.
Fashion magazines, sure, but all kinds are there.
For some reason, Mu was in the lineup!
I thought "I wanna read it!" but...
When getting washed at the end...
Slightly erotic magazines are in there.
Wisdom of age is built different.
I came home without reading it.
Next month I want to read it.
The hair salon Subaru goes to, what is it?
That lineup is a huge mystery lineup.
Subaru usually reads dog and cat magazines.
I'm not buying them, but I look at dog and cat magazines to feel like I bought one.
Then I read travel magazines to feel like I traveled, then it ends.
Doesn't Orange Page make you hungry?
"Your life will be completely taken over by the dog."
But Subaru had both a dog and cat...
It kept pointing its butt at Subaru's face.
"Why does this guy keep pointing his butt at me?"
"Gimme gimme, give it, give me food."
Eh, that was proof of trust?
Lying down in the living room...
Was I being looked down on?
Maybe it thought we were the same species.
The cat, like, in Subaru's room...
There's a small side table there.
And there's a small gap there.
In that gap, it stays forever and never comes out.
Made that the cat's sleeping place...
It basks in the sun forever.
Doesn't come out from under the bed.
Well, the cat didn't smell as bad.
What should we have done about that?
Eh? Then maybe the shampoo smell was...
There was a time like that.
